ctFnbCSMACDTable.name: ctFnbCSMACDTable
ctFnbCSMACDTable.description: A list of entries that provide connection status of CSMA/CD subsystems, for the FNB.

ctFnbCSMACDEntry.name: ctFnbCSMACDEntry
ctFnbCSMACDEntry.description: An entry in the ctFnbCSMACDTable containing objects that provide FNB connection status for a CSMA/CD subsystem.

ctFnbCSMACDIndex.name: ctFnbCSMACDIndex
ctFnbCSMACDIndex.description: An unique value for each CSMACD subsystem. Its value ranges between 1 and chassisSlots. The value for each interface must remain constant, at least, from one re-initialization of the entity's network management system to the next re-initialization.

ctFnbConnect.name: ctFnbConnect
ctFnbConnect.description: Denotes the connection status of the CSMA/CD board to the inter-RIC bus. The values of 1, 2, and 4 define connection status of connect for the subsystem, values 5 and 6 define connection status of subnet connect for the subsystem, value 8 is defined as a front panel connection on the module, and a value of 3 defines disconnect status.

ctFnbPortChanges.name: ctFnbPortChanges
ctFnbPortChanges.description: Denotes the number of times any port on the given MIM has changed it's connection to the inter-RIC bus.

ctFnbPortConnectTable.name: ctFnbPortConnectTable
ctFnbPortConnectTable.description: This table is used to control port association on ethernet devices. Only those boards that support port switching will be listed in this table.

ctFnbPortConnectEntry.name: ctFnbPortConnectEntry
ctFnbPortConnectEntry.description: Describes a specific port connection entry.

ctFnbPortConnectBoardIndex.name: ctFnbPortConnectBoardIndex
ctFnbPortConnectBoardIndex.description: An instance of a board for which this port assignment relationship exists.

ctFnbPortConnectPortIndex.name: ctFnbPortConnectPortIndex
ctFnbPortConnectPortIndex.description: An instance of a port for which this assignment relationship exists.

ctFnbPortConnectPortAssignment.name: ctFnbPortConnectPortAssignment
ctFnbPortConnectPortAssignment.description: The specific channel that the port is assigned.

ctFnbPortCompID.name: ctFnbPortCompID
ctFnbPortCompID.description: This is the component ID as defined in the chassis MIB that this port is associated with. These components will be repeater components.

ctFnbPortConnectionChanges.name: ctFnbPortConnectionChanges
ctFnbPortConnectionChanges.description: Maintains the number of times any port within the mangement domain of this MIM changes it's port assignment.
